sample.topic: Adding documents to your Cart on TexasFile
sample.description: My Cart is a feature on TexasFile allowing users to purchase and download multiple documents in a single zip file including an Excel index report. To add docs to your Cart, click the Cart icon in search results then visit the Cart page.

sample.topic: Looking for information about a Texas Driver's License?
sample.description: TexasFile does not provide information about driver's licenses. For more information, contact the Texas Department of Public Safety using the link below.
Criminal records are not available on TexasFile. To locate this information, contact the District Clerk's office by using our County Directory below.

term: how do I contact a county clerk
how do I contact a district clerk

sample.description: Birth certificates are not available on TexasFile. To obtain birth certificate contact the County Clerk's office using our county directory below.
Death certificates are not available on TexasFile. To obtain a death certificate contact the County Clerk's office using our county directory below.
Marriage certificates are not available on TexasFile. To obtain a marriage certificate contact the County Clerk's office using our county directory below.
